..TEXT:
Those who argue that Cato is being overzealous should pay
closer attention to this strong charge he makes against the negligent
spirits.  Whatever the 'slough' (^scoglio~) signifies, their adherence
to it prevents their seeing God.  In the world of the ^Commedia~ that
can never be a slight problem.
